nodes.bodyText:
"Add an ..." sounds like the PR description copied as Javadoc comment here. Shouldn't this be something like "Interpreter returns an instance of {@code IncompleteData} if an object is an instance of {@link PartialMessage}" .
I am assuming PartialMessage is defined somewhere.

nodes.bodyText: Thanks for the review! PartialMessage is defined internally, and from API-wise we don't need it at this moment. Regarding to the comment, We copied them from the internal CEL lib, but I agreed that the original comments could be improved, and yours are much better... @cindyxue Can you please update them? Thanks!
